**Assignment overview**

This program uses a loop to make an LED turn  Red, Green, Blue. It relies on a variable loopcount to make the LED light up every 10th loop count. Each color flashes 3 times before it moves onto the next color.

**Tip or trick**
Make sure to make the delay long enough so the light actually turns on and stays on long enough to be noticable before it turns off. 
